ты: &lt;a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/nikitatunes/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;https://www.linkedin.com/in/nikitatunes/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;TG Никиты: &lt;a href="http://t.me/airtuna" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;t.me/airtuna&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
